<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>nǐ yǒng yuǎn shì wǒ de fù 迦南821</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 nǐ yǒng yǒng yuǎn yuǎn shì wǒ de fù, wǒ yǒng yǒng yuǎn yuǎn shì nǐ de hái zi. suī rán
 wǒ liú làng dào tiān yá, fàn zuì yuǎn lí nǐ. nǐ réng tiān tiān zhàn zài mén kǒu zhāng wàng, nǐ
 hǎn zhe wǒ de míng zì. huí lái ba de de hái zi, wǒ zài yuǎn fāng dōu yǐ tīng jiàn. fù a
 wǒ zhèng yào xiàng nǐ huí zhuǎn, kuài kuài huí dào nǐ de shēn biān. yīn wèi wǒ shì nǐ de hái zi. fù a
 wǒ zhèng yào xiàng nǐ huí zhuǎn, wǒ de zuì nǐ dōu yǐ shè miǎn. yīn wèi wǒ shì nǐ de hái zi.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
